 also found in Mt. Wilhelm. Consequently, despite that the study was restricted to one mountain in PNG, it demonstrates how basic inventory surveys can be used to address ecological questions in other similar and undisturbed tropical mountains.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Sivault, Elise", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Amick, Pita K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Armstrong, Kyle N.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Novotny, Vojtech", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sam, Katerina", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/80da7fdb1c282b0eb5a76400e6850ff7", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/3dd37912c787a47d35e90e8ec84339aa34daf0a1d5209f006fb0fab88342d6db", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/R4YI3J3S", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/R4YI3J3S", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/ec3ffc15a67789da888cc7320687452e!/b54576-57043", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "81-94", "title": "Biotropica", "volume": "55"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/80da7fdb1c282b0eb5a76400e6850ff7"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:R4YI3J3S"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/btp.13161"}], "com